         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="TireeandMull_TireeBarrapolHMacLeanweather-d0e1346">
            <form>
               <orth>[general sayings or proverbs 5]</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Beanntan a’ sealltainn (Tiree instead of  ‘a’ coimhead’) na’s fhaisge ort na tha iad ann da rireadh.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="TireeandMull_TireeBarrapolHMacLeanweather-d0e1352">
